      • getMapValueIndex

        protected int[] getMapValueIndex(org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.vector.MapColumnVector mapV,
                                 org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.exec.vector.VectorizedRowBatch batch)
        The index array of MapColumnVector is used to get the value from MapColumnVector based on the index, the following are the steps to get it: 1. Get the current key which is a scalar or from a ColumnVector. 2. Compare the current key and the key from MapColumnVector. 3. Set the index of MapColumnVector to the result array if the keys are same.
